WEBVTT

00:12.250 --> 00:18.460
[2009]

00:24.830 --> 00:25.480
Chuan,

00:27.070 --> 00:28.600
I want to ask you a question.

00:29.760 --> 00:30.640
Tell me...

00:33.070 --> 00:34.600
What's the scariest thing?

00:35.260 --> 00:38.430
Your feet stinking up the place every day
is scary enough.

00:38.430 --> 00:39.090
Be serious.

00:41.310 --> 00:42.780
Mice, snakes.

00:43.320 --> 00:44.240
Not that kind.

00:46.630 --> 00:48.560
What's the most terrifying thing?

00:50.030 --> 00:50.750
Death?

00:52.430 --> 00:53.550
Not that either.

00:54.240 --> 00:55.320
Let me rephrase it.

00:56.670 --> 00:57.880
Hypothetically—

00:58.000 --> 00:59.640
let's say a person's whole life

00:59.640 --> 01:01.000
has already

01:01.000 --> 01:02.000
been written out.

01:02.200 --> 01:03.280
It's already set.

01:04.510 --> 01:07.770
And you could know in advance
what's going to happen to you.

01:07.870 --> 01:09.070
Would you want to know

01:09.710 --> 01:10.560
or not?

01:13.230 --> 01:14.840
Hey, is there anything wrong
with your brain?

01:14.840 --> 01:16.280
How could it be set?

01:16.360 --> 01:18.050
Hypothetically.

01:22.120 --> 01:22.950
I wouldn't want to know.

01:22.950 --> 01:24.400
It wouldn't be fun anymore.

01:24.400 --> 01:25.200
Why?

01:25.680 --> 01:27.190
If you could know,

01:27.430 --> 01:28.280
you'd know

01:29.070 --> 01:30.840
what bad things are going to happen.

01:30.840 --> 01:32.300
and avoid them in advance.

01:32.350 --> 01:33.150
Isn't that good?

01:33.150 --> 01:34.880
Alright, then I'd want to know.

01:35.150 --> 01:36.150
Wait, that's not right.

01:36.150 --> 01:37.680
Didn't you say it's already set?

01:37.680 --> 01:39.080
Then how could I avoid it?

01:39.400 --> 01:41.070
Like in those

01:41.120 --> 01:42.650
time-traveling TV series,

01:42.940 --> 01:45.070
they already knew what was going to happen

01:45.070 --> 01:47.039
and tried their best to change it,

01:47.070 --> 01:49.000
but the outcome was still the same.

01:49.530 --> 01:50.590
It hasn't changed.

01:50.780 --> 01:52.870
You can't change anything. It's pointless.

01:52.870 --> 01:53.729
What about you?

01:54.070 --> 01:57.070
Would you want to know or not?

01:59.590 --> 02:01.070
What kind of stuff have you been reading?

02:01.070 --> 02:02.480
Mystery novels.

02:05.430 --> 02:06.040
Chuan,

02:07.760 --> 02:08.800
I just feel

02:08.800 --> 02:09.870
that people

02:10.310 --> 02:11.640
are too insignificant.

02:12.120 --> 02:13.120
They know nothing

02:14.400 --> 02:16.060
and can't see the big picture.

02:16.520 --> 02:17.280
All they can see is

02:17.280 --> 02:20.140
what exists within their own
limited perspective.

02:20.400 --> 02:23.200
So sometimes,
it's really scary to think about it.

02:23.710 --> 02:25.120
It's like fate

02:25.120 --> 02:26.320
has blindfolded you.

02:28.000 --> 02:29.760
Real life is the same.

02:29.960 --> 02:31.290
Every day is uncertain.

02:32.710 --> 02:35.310
So I know
what the most terrifying thing is now.

02:35.360 --> 02:37.020
The unpredictability of life

02:37.150 --> 02:38.810
is the most terrifying thing.

02:43.520 --> 02:44.150
What?

02:45.630 --> 02:46.280
Sis,

02:46.900 --> 02:47.900
I realize you

02:48.790 --> 02:49.590
have grown up.

02:50.630 --> 02:51.750
I just hope

02:52.150 --> 02:54.400
that my life will be smooth and easy,

02:54.750 --> 02:56.630
like a straight, steady river,

02:57.030 --> 02:58.470
without wind or waves,

02:58.870 --> 03:01.000
smooth and steady all the way.

03:03.770 --> 03:05.770
Life is hard—that's normal.

03:06.630 --> 03:08.490
Nothing is certain in this world.

03:09.000 --> 03:10.060
Live in the moment.

03:10.690 --> 03:12.010
What you feel right now

03:12.080 --> 03:13.080
matters most.

03:16.470 --> 03:18.000
Alright, stop overthinking.

03:18.000 --> 03:19.530
I'll always be here for you.

03:20.030 --> 03:20.560
Here,

03:20.750 --> 03:21.400
read it.

03:22.360 --> 03:23.360
Okay!

03:26.310 --> 03:27.640
Life is unpredictable.

03:29.280 --> 03:30.430
Live in the moment.

03:33.870 --> 03:36.000
I trust what I'm feeling right now.

03:38.620 --> 03:39.680
Let's get married.

03:41.710 --> 03:42.520
Okay.

03:43.470 --> 03:44.530
Let's get married.

05:03.960 --> 05:09.720
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

05:10.130 --> 05:12.470
[Episode 13]

05:44.110 --> 05:45.240
Jiang Cheng, right?

05:46.230 --> 05:47.360
The game now begins.

05:57.750 --> 05:58.720
Cheng.

06:01.750 --> 06:02.880
What does this mean?

06:03.480 --> 06:05.460
You can't bring dangerous items
to meet Old Scorpion.

06:05.460 --> 06:06.660
Old Scorpion is here?

06:10.120 --> 06:11.920
You're not Old Scorpion, right?

06:14.480 --> 06:15.480
What do you think?

06:21.330 --> 06:23.130
You took our phones when we left,

06:23.240 --> 06:24.680
and now you're searching us.
What's this supposed to mean?

06:24.680 --> 06:25.360
Dahua.

06:25.480 --> 06:26.360
Shut up.

06:36.159 --> 06:37.560
You're taking this, too?

06:42.360 --> 06:43.159
It's okay now.

06:44.159 --> 06:44.730
Let's go.

07:06.430 --> 07:07.070
Hold on.

07:09.800 --> 07:10.800
What's your name?

07:10.950 --> 07:11.720
Jiang Cheng.

07:12.480 --> 07:13.600
I heard from Mr. He

07:13.720 --> 07:15.120
that you used to be a cop.

07:15.600 --> 07:16.190
Yeah.

07:16.800 --> 07:18.680
Before he sent you here,

07:18.920 --> 07:20.360
did he tell you

07:20.800 --> 07:22.930
that Old Scorpion hates cops the most?

07:39.510 --> 07:40.270
Is it fun?

07:40.800 --> 07:41.510
Not bad.

07:43.120 --> 07:44.680
Looks like Mr. He

07:44.870 --> 07:47.240
finally has someone with guts under him.

07:48.510 --> 07:50.500
I remember his cousin,

07:50.600 --> 07:51.310
Lai San—

07:51.630 --> 07:53.090
Before I even fired a shot,

07:53.720 --> 07:56.270
he pissed himself on the spot.

07:56.720 --> 07:58.190
Until now, I still can't forget

07:58.190 --> 07:59.560
the stench on him.

08:02.000 --> 08:03.130
I'm no match for you.

08:03.190 --> 08:04.390
I give up, Godfather.

08:05.510 --> 08:07.570
Do you know how to play Chinese chess?

08:09.600 --> 08:10.600
Let him come over.

08:11.990 --> 08:12.570
Come.

08:28.920 --> 08:29.430
Sit.

08:41.030 --> 08:41.960
Red moves first.

08:49.440 --> 08:50.550
I heard

08:51.150 --> 08:53.210
you've been in the limelight lately.

08:54.010 --> 08:56.010
The bosses gave me the opportunity.

08:58.840 --> 09:00.370
Why did you stop being a cop?

09:00.600 --> 09:02.720
I got in the way of someone's promotion

09:02.720 --> 09:03.520
and got set up.

09:08.670 --> 09:10.000
It's not really a secret.

09:10.000 --> 09:11.130
It was a badger game.

09:11.390 --> 09:12.510
During the investigation,

09:12.510 --> 09:14.240
a bag of white powder was found on me.

09:14.240 --> 09:15.870
Not only was I kicked
out of the police force,

09:15.870 --> 09:18.270
but I also did 3 years
in prison for nothing.

09:19.000 --> 09:20.460
You were framed by others.

09:20.840 --> 09:23.790
You were forced onto this path.

09:24.720 --> 09:25.780
Just for the money.

09:41.660 --> 09:43.260
Have you ever killed anyone?

09:48.790 --> 09:50.250
Have you ever killed a cop?

09:53.670 --> 09:54.930
I've heard about this.

09:55.360 --> 09:56.960
Cops who fall into your hands

09:57.000 --> 09:57.860
have no way out.

10:01.000 --> 10:02.440
I mean you.

10:04.550 --> 10:05.960
Seems like you haven't.

10:07.630 --> 10:08.750
I'm just a nobody.

10:09.270 --> 10:10.870
I'm nowhere near your level.

10:12.630 --> 10:14.510
But I think sometimes

10:14.510 --> 10:17.310
a living person is much more useful
than a dead one.

10:17.320 --> 10:18.870
I work for Mr. He.

10:19.610 --> 10:21.240
Sometimes, an extra friendship

10:21.240 --> 10:23.510
means another way to make money.

10:24.390 --> 10:26.630
To carry weight on both sides of the law,

10:27.080 --> 10:28.670
you can't just rely on being ruthless.

10:28.670 --> 10:29.800
You also need to have

10:30.750 --> 10:32.610
the capacity to tolerate others.

10:32.670 --> 10:33.670
What do you think?

10:41.320 --> 10:42.920
Are you telling me what to do?

10:43.330 --> 10:44.730
I didn't mean that at all.

10:57.440 --> 10:58.240
Good.

10:59.910 --> 11:00.720
Good.

11:01.550 --> 11:02.360
Good.

11:06.150 --> 11:08.280
I need someone like you working for me.

11:10.000 --> 11:11.440
What do you want me

11:11.540 --> 11:12.770
to do for you?

11:30.840 --> 11:31.870
Kill this man,

11:36.200 --> 11:38.150
and I'll give you a bright future.

11:52.550 --> 11:53.630
Position 2 is confirmed.

11:53.630 --> 11:55.490
They are unloading goods inside.

11:55.550 --> 11:56.200
Copy that.

11:57.150 --> 11:57.810
Leader Yao.

12:09.030 --> 12:10.430
Where is the backup team?

12:10.600 --> 12:12.660
SWAT will reach the pier in 5 minutes.

12:13.600 --> 12:15.360
What is He Wu doing? Where is he going?

12:15.360 --> 12:16.030
We tracked him

12:16.030 --> 12:17.320
near an abandoned factory.

12:17.320 --> 12:19.030
It's the opposite direction from Jingang.

12:19.030 --> 12:20.790
It's on Beijiang Road in the northeast.

12:20.790 --> 12:21.910
Keep an eye on him.

12:22.270 --> 12:23.870
Report any situation at once.

12:23.870 --> 12:24.510
Copy that.

12:24.790 --> 12:25.510
Stay close.

12:32.270 --> 12:32.910
Wan,

12:33.160 --> 12:34.750
is there any movement from He Wu?

12:34.750 --> 12:35.960
Follow my location.

12:36.360 --> 12:37.000
Okay.

13:04.150 --> 13:05.080
Boss, you...

13:21.720 --> 13:22.600
So,

13:23.720 --> 13:25.650
we're not doing business tonight?

13:25.870 --> 13:26.730
What business?

13:31.360 --> 13:32.630
You mean

13:33.510 --> 13:35.060
the goods at Jingang Wharf?

13:40.870 --> 13:42.480
All the bros here know

13:43.360 --> 13:45.440
a batch of goods

13:45.440 --> 13:47.170
will be shipped there tonight.

13:51.790 --> 13:53.000
Hey, this...

13:53.000 --> 13:54.240
This intel is fake.

14:00.510 --> 14:02.350
We set this up just to…

14:06.150 --> 14:07.390
just to kill him.

14:10.550 --> 14:12.200
Just to kill him!

14:24.870 --> 14:25.600
Hello.

14:25.600 --> 14:26.030
Long time no see.

14:26.030 --> 14:26.790
Hello.

14:30.550 --> 14:31.630
Leader Yao. Leader Yao.

14:31.630 --> 14:33.910
The first batch
of reinforcements is in place.

14:33.910 --> 14:34.550
Okay.

14:34.870 --> 14:37.080
Act only after confirming the drug deal.

14:37.080 --> 14:38.210
Wait for my command.

14:38.240 --> 14:38.870
Copy that.

14:50.940 --> 14:51.580
Move out.

14:54.120 --> 14:54.750
Freeze!

14:54.750 --> 14:55.300
Police!

14:55.330 --> 14:55.780
Stop!

14:55.800 --> 14:56.370
Stop!

14:57.080 --> 14:57.630
Stop!

14:57.870 --> 14:58.440
Get down!

14:58.460 --> 14:59.010
Stop!

15:22.080 --> 15:22.630
Report.

15:22.650 --> 15:24.140
It's all flour. No drugs.

15:31.030 --> 15:32.160
Something's wrong.

15:32.510 --> 15:34.110
Tell them to pull out, quick!

16:01.070 --> 16:01.980
Tell me,

16:02.320 --> 16:04.370
why so many police

16:04.480 --> 16:06.000
showed up to raid

16:07.140 --> 16:08.810
our cargo ship full of timber

16:08.840 --> 16:10.290
at Jingang Wharf?

16:10.550 --> 16:12.210
The police really went there?

16:13.270 --> 16:14.320
A lot of them.

16:14.720 --> 16:15.910
It seems we really

16:16.340 --> 16:17.600
have a mole here.

16:19.080 --> 16:20.080
Who could they be?

16:34.360 --> 16:36.360
A mole...

16:38.390 --> 16:39.360
A mole.

16:45.910 --> 16:47.970
Wan, you guys pin down He Wu first.

16:48.200 --> 16:49.150
Yes. Move out.

17:22.849 --> 17:23.650
Sniper!

17:23.680 --> 17:24.880
Everyone, take cover!

17:24.880 --> 17:25.690
Are you okay?

17:25.720 --> 17:26.400
I'm fine.

17:26.680 --> 17:27.480
I can hold on.

17:34.680 --> 17:35.480
It's the cops.

17:35.830 --> 17:36.480
Boss.

17:36.480 --> 17:37.720
Is there another exit?

17:37.720 --> 17:38.480
Follow me.

17:41.980 --> 17:42.610
Let's go.

17:50.530 --> 17:51.530
We are ambushed.

17:51.650 --> 17:53.910
Requesting backup. Requesting backup.

17:58.590 --> 17:59.240
Senior,

17:59.690 --> 18:00.970
they came prepared.

18:01.240 --> 18:02.440
It's not an easy task.

18:03.110 --> 18:03.960
Stay here.

18:03.960 --> 18:04.880
Protect yourself.

18:04.880 --> 18:05.780
Where are you going?

18:05.780 --> 18:07.070
I'm going to draw him out.

18:07.070 --> 18:07.720
No.

18:07.770 --> 18:08.900
It's too dangerous!

18:13.270 --> 18:13.920
Senior.

18:28.870 --> 18:30.020
Interesting.

18:32.790 --> 18:33.720
Here, quick!

18:41.680 --> 18:42.350
Quick!

20:28.360 --> 20:29.270
Interesting.

20:32.620 --> 20:33.980
Very interesting.

21:20.200 --> 21:20.920
Go!

21:20.920 --> 21:22.720
Old Scorpion is waiting for you.

21:40.880 --> 21:41.640
Hurry.

21:58.110 --> 21:59.720
If you want to live,

22:00.740 --> 22:02.270
I suggest you stop chasing.

22:04.270 --> 22:05.750
You might as well shoot me.

22:06.850 --> 22:07.860
Jiang Cheng.

22:26.640 --> 22:27.590
Why are you here?

22:28.200 --> 22:29.270
Don't touch me!

22:29.960 --> 22:30.920
Stop chasing.

22:34.080 --> 22:35.270
Don't touch me.

22:44.880 --> 22:46.540
I should be the one asking you.

22:47.240 --> 22:48.550
Why are you here?

22:50.160 --> 22:51.500
Why is it you?

22:52.240 --> 22:53.070
Jiang Cheng.

22:55.200 --> 22:57.400
Are you really dealing drugs with them?

22:58.990 --> 23:00.830
Why are you doing this? Answer me.

23:00.830 --> 23:02.830
Stop talking. Stop talking about it.

23:02.830 --> 23:03.920
Why?

23:04.570 --> 23:05.810
Do you know

23:05.830 --> 23:07.480
the man you just let go

23:08.000 --> 23:09.240
was?

23:09.680 --> 23:11.960
Do you know they kill police officers?

23:12.480 --> 23:13.590
Do you know

23:13.590 --> 23:15.000
the people you're dealing drugs with

23:15.000 --> 23:16.110
killed Chuan?

23:19.400 --> 23:22.160
Do you know they killed Chuan?

23:22.160 --> 23:23.790
They killed Chuan!

23:24.350 --> 23:26.030
Do you know that?

23:35.270 --> 23:36.530
I know.

23:59.240 --> 23:59.790
Zhou Jin,

24:00.920 --> 24:01.650
are you okay?

24:02.160 --> 24:02.760
Hansheng,

24:04.290 --> 24:05.350
how did you find me?

24:07.110 --> 24:07.710
I'm sorry.

24:07.790 --> 24:08.590
I'm late.

24:31.070 --> 24:32.590
Did Chuan let you down,

24:33.360 --> 24:34.750
or did I let you down?

24:43.000 --> 24:43.750
Do you know

24:43.750 --> 24:45.440
the man you just let go

24:45.440 --> 24:46.840
killed police officers?

24:47.280 --> 24:48.200
Do you know

24:48.200 --> 24:49.480
the people you're dealing drugs with

24:49.480 --> 24:50.720
killed Chuan?

25:59.720 --> 26:00.830
The tetanus shot hurts a bit.

26:00.830 --> 26:02.230
Bear with it for a moment.

26:11.270 --> 26:12.400
Ready for stitches.

27:05.790 --> 27:07.440
Officer Jiang!

27:27.400 --> 27:29.030
Officer Jiang!

27:31.110 --> 27:32.150
Killing people—

27:32.920 --> 27:33.780
Is it exciting?

27:33.960 --> 27:36.510
Officer Jiang has deep insights

27:36.510 --> 27:38.160
in the field of psychology.

27:38.160 --> 27:39.440
Can't you understand my work?

27:39.440 --> 27:40.420
There's no other way.

27:40.420 --> 27:41.480
If I don't kill them,

27:41.480 --> 27:42.480
I can't calm down.

27:42.640 --> 27:43.440
Just like you!

27:43.510 --> 27:44.200
Officer Jiang.

27:44.200 --> 27:44.920
Right now,

27:45.070 --> 27:47.310
do you want to kill me?

27:47.790 --> 27:48.200
Kill me!

27:48.200 --> 27:48.790
Officer Jiang!

27:48.790 --> 27:49.480
Come on.

27:49.480 --> 27:50.640
Don't suppress your desires!

27:50.640 --> 27:51.550
Kill me.

27:51.640 --> 27:52.200
Kill me.

27:52.270 --> 27:53.350
Kill me.

27:53.350 --> 27:54.790
For the girl you love,

27:54.790 --> 27:56.070
kill me!

28:13.310 --> 28:14.880
Watch your diet recently.

28:15.070 --> 28:16.030
Don't make big movements,

28:16.030 --> 28:17.630
so you don't tear your wound.

28:18.110 --> 28:19.240
Change the dressing in 3 days,

28:19.240 --> 28:21.100
and remove the stitches in 7 days.

28:21.110 --> 28:21.680
Got it?

28:22.440 --> 28:23.200
Thank you.

28:23.400 --> 28:24.330
You're welcome.

28:24.640 --> 28:26.710
Your husband went to the pharmacy
to get your medicine.

28:26.710 --> 28:28.110
You can wait for him here.

28:41.920 --> 28:42.640
Mentor.

28:42.750 --> 28:43.590
What is it?

28:43.720 --> 28:44.590
Are you alone?

28:46.240 --> 28:46.920
Go ahead.

28:47.680 --> 28:49.280
Has Leader Yao been rescued?

28:54.880 --> 28:56.210
We're still searching.

28:56.630 --> 28:59.160
How could you go looking
for the sniper alone?

28:59.510 --> 29:01.230
What if you didn't make it back?

29:01.230 --> 29:02.960
It was Jiang Cheng who saved me.

29:04.240 --> 29:04.720
What?

29:05.350 --> 29:07.160
He escorted the sniper away,

29:07.480 --> 29:09.000
which basically saved me.

29:09.000 --> 29:09.640
Chief Tan!

29:12.440 --> 29:13.200
Okay, I got it.

29:13.200 --> 29:14.880
Chief Tan, it's a call
from the Provincial Bureau.

29:14.880 --> 29:15.680
Write a report first.

29:15.680 --> 29:16.940
I'll talk to you later.

29:18.270 --> 29:18.750
Okay.

29:32.510 --> 29:33.040
Zhou Jin.

29:35.820 --> 29:36.480
How are you?

29:37.070 --> 29:38.130
Does it still hurt?

29:41.400 --> 29:41.930
I'm fine.

30:20.460 --> 30:22.260
Do you have something to tell me?

30:27.830 --> 30:28.920
I'm a little tired.

30:59.950 --> 31:00.710
Zhou Jin.

31:02.750 --> 31:04.210
Don't do this again, okay?

31:05.310 --> 31:07.060
Before you do anything dangerous,

31:07.060 --> 31:08.010
think of me.

31:12.510 --> 31:13.440
Okay.

31:26.200 --> 31:26.880
By the way,

31:28.830 --> 31:30.110
how did you find me?

31:30.830 --> 31:32.030
Why are you able

31:33.060 --> 31:34.930
to arrive so quickly every time?

31:36.310 --> 31:38.170
Because you always make me worry.

31:38.480 --> 31:39.700
Hurry up and brush your teeth.

31:39.700 --> 31:40.590
Then, go to bed.

31:40.990 --> 31:41.990
You must be tired.

32:08.920 --> 32:09.550
Hansheng.

32:10.920 --> 32:13.250
5 years ago, I let you
and your master down,

32:13.510 --> 32:14.440
especially you.

32:15.430 --> 32:16.640
I am deeply sorry.

32:17.610 --> 32:19.090
If it really is a trap,

32:19.750 --> 32:21.080
I will follow your path.

32:21.900 --> 32:23.010
Dead or alive,

32:23.250 --> 32:24.710
I'll bring back the clues.

32:26.180 --> 32:27.070
You and Zhou Jin

32:28.160 --> 32:29.220
must never give up.

32:39.060 --> 32:39.790
Prof.

32:40.730 --> 32:41.730
I was wrong.

32:42.640 --> 32:44.270
Qi Yan is not dead.

32:45.920 --> 32:47.600
Now, Leader Yao is in trouble.

32:59.410 --> 33:00.560
I heard about it.

33:01.520 --> 33:02.840
Don't overthink it.

33:03.880 --> 33:05.270
Be careful.

33:37.790 --> 33:38.520
Jiang Cheng.

33:42.680 --> 33:43.410
Jiang Cheng.

34:12.800 --> 34:14.550
Pass it! Pass it!

34:14.670 --> 34:16.510
Pass the ball!

34:16.510 --> 34:18.570
Why dribble if you can't get past him?

34:22.440 --> 34:23.280
Jin.

34:29.179 --> 34:30.570
Why are you here?

34:35.070 --> 34:35.800
I'm back,

34:35.949 --> 34:36.510
Jin.

34:44.710 --> 34:45.310
Jin.

34:46.850 --> 34:47.850
It was my fault.

34:48.920 --> 34:50.070
Don't cry anymore.

34:55.510 --> 34:56.239
Jiang Cheng!

34:57.510 --> 34:58.510
Jiang Cheng!

35:07.380 --> 35:08.170
Jiang Cheng.

35:09.910 --> 35:10.720
Jiang Cheng.

35:19.030 --> 35:20.430
Did you have a nightmare?

35:22.730 --> 35:23.480
I'm fine.

35:30.490 --> 35:31.890
What did you dream about?

35:36.230 --> 35:37.110
Nothing.

35:49.590 --> 35:50.520
Go back to sleep.

36:51.640 --> 36:52.930
Officer Jiang,

36:54.230 --> 36:55.280
does your girl

36:56.390 --> 36:58.020
really care about you?

38:13.040 --> 38:14.440
Why aren't you sleeping?

38:20.280 --> 38:21.110
I saw

38:24.340 --> 38:25.530
Jiang Cheng today.

38:34.760 --> 38:36.760
I almost got killed

38:39.690 --> 38:40.960
chasing that sniper.

38:43.960 --> 38:45.690
It was Jiang Cheng who saved me.

39:12.230 --> 39:14.400
Leader Yao received a reliable tip

39:14.750 --> 39:16.680
that there will be a major drug deal

39:16.930 --> 39:18.330
at Jingang Wharf today.

39:19.000 --> 39:19.960
So Leader Yao

39:20.190 --> 39:22.320
will personally lead a team there
to make the arrest.

39:22.320 --> 39:24.120
However, before your next move,

39:24.780 --> 39:25.550
I hope

39:26.190 --> 39:27.650
you can look into someone.

39:28.070 --> 39:28.480
Who?

39:29.190 --> 39:29.920
Jiang Cheng.

39:30.710 --> 39:31.280
Why?

39:33.030 --> 39:35.360
Aren't you supposed to ask
who he is first?

39:54.770 --> 39:56.120
Attention, all units.

39:56.190 --> 39:58.800
Maintain current duty status for 42 hours.

39:59.190 --> 40:01.630
Increase patrol frequency at the station.

40:02.070 --> 40:04.670
Thoroughly investigate
every suspicious person.

40:04.670 --> 40:05.960
Seal off Hengyun Logistics,

40:05.960 --> 40:06.920
Phoenix Fire Bar,

40:06.920 --> 40:09.760
and other businesses
closely related to the suspects.

40:09.760 --> 40:12.710
Conduct a full investigation
into their connections.

40:12.710 --> 40:15.060
Any information related
to Comrade Yao Weihai

40:15.060 --> 40:16.360
must be reported immediately.

40:16.360 --> 40:18.150
Treat every clue seriously.

40:18.190 --> 40:19.250
Verify carefully.

40:44.840 --> 40:46.880
Their target was very clear,

40:46.880 --> 40:48.400
and they moved very fast.

40:48.760 --> 40:50.480
The tunnel was dug in advance.

40:50.550 --> 40:53.230
The entrance was
in the container warehouse.

40:53.440 --> 40:55.670
The container warehouse was just a cover.

40:55.670 --> 40:56.510
After the explosion,

40:56.510 --> 40:58.320
there was brief chaos.

40:58.590 --> 41:00.040
That's when Leader Yao

41:00.140 --> 41:01.100
was pulled into the tunnel.

41:00.240 --> 41:04.250
[Director Wang Pengze]

41:01.440 --> 41:02.920
They also left some cannon fodder

41:02.920 --> 41:04.320
to resist the police.

41:04.670 --> 41:06.840
It was actually just to buy time.

41:07.070 --> 41:08.390
Where does this tunnel lead?

41:08.390 --> 41:11.140
It leads directly
to the city's sewer system.

41:11.800 --> 41:12.400
By the way,

41:12.710 --> 41:14.190
after they left the tunnel,

41:14.190 --> 41:16.120
they detonated explosives twice.

41:16.480 --> 41:18.550
The entrance
has collapsed from the explosion.

41:18.550 --> 41:21.010
Our SWAT officers
were almost buried alive.

41:23.320 --> 41:25.150
Leader Yao has been missing

41:25.360 --> 41:26.840
for more than 48 hours.

41:27.090 --> 41:28.180
If this

41:28.280 --> 41:29.030
really is

41:29.440 --> 41:31.000
a trap set by Qi Yan,

41:31.930 --> 41:34.000
the consequences could be catastrophic.

41:34.000 --> 41:35.190
When Jiang Hansheng told me

41:35.190 --> 41:37.850
that there was a fifth person
in this warehouse,

41:38.190 --> 41:39.480
I got chills, too.

41:41.710 --> 41:42.550
It seems they are

41:42.550 --> 41:45.150
getting revenge
for what happened 5 years ago.

41:45.190 --> 41:46.050
Director Wang.

41:46.190 --> 41:48.120
How is your progress in Huaiguang?

41:48.820 --> 41:50.340
Qi Yan

41:50.770 --> 41:52.430
is quite a mysterious figure.

41:53.110 --> 41:54.110
I need

41:55.280 --> 41:56.800
to sort this whole thing out
from the beginning

41:56.800 --> 41:58.710
based on the new clues we have now.

41:59.550 --> 42:01.010
The top priority right now

42:01.040 --> 42:03.200
is to find Yao

42:03.230 --> 42:04.560
and the undercover cop.

42:04.800 --> 42:05.280
Okay.

42:05.840 --> 42:06.570
Don't worry,

42:06.630 --> 42:08.430
we will definitely try our best.

42:08.910 --> 42:09.510
Right now,

42:09.740 --> 42:11.000
you're carrying a heavy burden.

42:11.000 --> 42:11.960
You must hold on.

42:12.110 --> 42:12.710
Okay.

42:13.110 --> 42:13.970
Director Wang,

42:14.030 --> 42:15.880
if there is nothing else,
we'll leave it at that.

42:15.880 --> 42:17.110
If there is any new situation,

42:17.110 --> 42:18.970
I will report to you immediately.

42:19.070 --> 42:19.710
And,

42:19.880 --> 42:20.960
emphasize it to Jiang Hansheng

42:20.960 --> 42:22.090
and that little girl

42:22.400 --> 42:23.480
once again,

42:23.480 --> 42:25.760
make sure they are extra careful.

42:25.800 --> 42:26.660
Did you hear me?

42:27.110 --> 42:27.710
Okay.

42:28.070 --> 42:29.600
Zhou Jin is right next to me.

42:29.630 --> 42:30.400
Don't worry.

42:30.570 --> 42:31.880
Okay, let's keep in touch.

42:31.880 --> 42:32.510
Goodbye.

42:39.150 --> 42:41.210
Didn't you ask what the situation is?

42:41.550 --> 42:43.350
This is the situation right now.

42:44.590 --> 42:45.990
What did Director Wang just say

42:45.990 --> 42:47.280
about Leader Yao

42:47.680 --> 42:49.010
and the undercover cop?

42:50.000 --> 42:51.730
Before the Jingang operation,

42:51.880 --> 42:53.840
Leader Yao once told me the truth.

42:54.840 --> 42:57.170
Right now, there's an undercover officer

42:57.230 --> 42:59.030
inside Old Scorpion's
criminal organization.

42:59.030 --> 43:00.510
His code name is Cangfeng.

43:01.280 --> 43:03.480
He had been in one-way contact with him.

43:04.710 --> 43:05.510
Cangfeng?
